OL,5, The chief executive of Birmingham      
OL,6, Airport has been given a 49% pay rise, 
OL,7, angering trade unions.                 
OL,9,FNick Barton's annual wage has risen    
OL,10,Ffrom #399,000 to #595,000.             
OL,12,FIt comes as air travellers have been   
OL,13,Fexperiencing long delays and           
OL,14,Fcancellations.                         
OL,16,FJane Nellist, president of Coventry    
OL,17,FTrade Union Council, said the pay was  
OL,18,F"absolutely disgraceful", but airport  
OL,19,Fboard member John McNicholas said it   
OL,20,Fwas "paying the appropriate rate".     
